leaseToObject

Hashtable<K,V> leaseToObject
For each lease that covers our knowledge of a registrar, we have a lease listener that is waiting for notification of the lease being terminated. When it is terminated, we can use this table to find the corresponding registrar, and then we can tear down the remaining infrastructure for the lost registrar
